      "Name": "SCAR-SC \"Silent Authority\"",
      "ShortName": "SCAR-SC",
      "Description": "A compact SCAR platform rebuilt into the SCAR-SC configuration and chambered in .300 Blackout. Originally designed for special operations use, the shortened platform excels in tight environments and suppressed engagements. This particular rifle passed through Tony's workshop, where the gas system was tuned and the action refined for smoother automatic fire. Compact, controllable, and brutally efficient, the SCAR-SC 'Silent Authority' proves that power doesn't have to be loud."
